'''Jax Keyn''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] native of [[Chandrila/Legends|Chandrila]] and owned a [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] called the [[Blackjack (YT-1300 light freighter)|''Blackjack'']], with his [[Pilot/Legends|copilot]] [[Trillia (pilot)|Trillia]]. Shortly after [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] announced himself [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]], he was employed by a [[Con artist/Legends|con artist]] who he knew as [["Mouse" Temple]], to transport [[Mon Mothma/Legends|Mon Mothma]] from the [[Inner Rim/Legends|Inner Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Renor]] to the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]]. Several members of Mon Mothma's team were captured by [[Imperial Security Bureau/Legends|ISB]] agents, though Mothma herself escaped, only to be captured by [[Pel Talon]]. With both Jax and his ship placed on a Most Wanted list following these events, he and his crew escaped to [["Snakes' Den"|Snake's Den]], prior to an attempt to free Mon Mothma.

